The director of a Gold Coast clinic which is today performing a record 23 boob jobs has defended its 'Super Friday' stunt, after it copped criticism from local doctors who were concerned it trivialised medical procedures.

Christyna Kruczaj, the director of the CosMediTours clinic at Surfer's Paradise, told Daily Mail Australia the clinic was not like a production line.

