'It's very far from a factory line,' Ms Kruszaj said. 'Because of the numbers people are obviously tagging it as something demonic or something.'

'It's not a factory line, it's based on surgeons per theatre and when it's feasible for them to do so.'

Ms Kruczaj told Daily Mail Australia the record breaking breast augmentation attempt was being held to shine a spotlight on the Gold Coast as a destination for medical tourism.

