Ms Kruszaj said she had received support from the local community about her attempts to muscle in on the medical tourism market.

'The Gold Coast must be open to all kinds of tourism', she said, whether that be whale-watching for plastic surgery.

She said 'time will tell' whether the clinic will attempt to break today's record. 

